From 20381bb9734e607e391fa472f4148ba26ba6116b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Hariharan Basuthkar <hbasuthk@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 9 Jun 2025 19:39:03 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM: PROTOCOL: Define global 6GHz operating class table
 and CFIs
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

1) Add static CFIs for global opclasses 131–137.
2) Create mapping table for 6GHz opclasses with associated CFIs
   and metadata.
3) Enable lookup and filtering of opclasses for AFC request generation.

Tag: 6G_REGULATORY
Patch-dependency: none

Signed-off-by: Hariharan Basuthkar <hbasuthk@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/reg.c | 205 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/reg.h |  74 ++++++++++
 2 files changed, 279 insertions(+)

